447
00:22:00.276 --> 00:22:01.526 A:middle
when you saved state".

448
00:22:01.986 --> 00:22:04.996 A:middle
So by specifying a restoration
class, you're telling us

449
00:22:05.056 --> 00:22:08.576 A:middle
who we can ask to recreate
this object as needed.

450
00:22:09.076 --> 00:22:13.296 A:middle
And in the example
I'm showing you,

451
00:22:13.426 --> 00:22:14.976 A:middle
all these different pieces here,

