00:22:15.646 --> 00:22:18.786 A:middle
these filters are
actually created on demand,

453
00:22:18.926 --> 00:22:23.886 A:middle
and we'll see how
we can do that.

454
00:22:24.736 --> 00:22:26.676 A:middle
This protocol that you use

455
00:22:27.026 --> 00:22:28.816 A:middle
to create the object
is very simple.

456
00:22:29.216 --> 00:22:31.686 A:middle
So we've specified
a restoration Class.

457
00:22:32.026 --> 00:22:34.326 A:middle
When we're restoring state
and we need the object,

458
00:22:34.756 --> 00:22:36.086 A:middle
we call a class method,

