00:22:37.226 --> 00:22:39.346 A:middle
objectWithRestorationIdentifier
path,

460
00:22:39.346 --> 00:22:41.986 A:middle
and it gets passed
in two things.

461
00:22:42.686 --> 00:22:45.646 A:middle
We give it an array of
identifier components.

462
00:22:45.856 --> 00:22:48.656 A:middle
The last component in that
